	keywords: 'People in Search Engine Optimization, History of Search Engine Optimization, History of Search Engine Marketing,  Search Engine Optimization History, History of Internet Marketing, The History of SEO, History of SEO, History of SEM, Internet Marketing History, Bend Oregon SEO, SEO History, SEO Profiles'
